\section{Evaluation Protocol}
\label{sec:evaluation}
Aetherion’s progress is assessed along three axes:

\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.3em]
  \item \textbf{Cognitive Performance:} Benchmarks on reasoning, multimodal synthesis, hypothesis generation.
  \item \textbf{Energy Efficiency:} $\eta = Q/E$ measured in \emph{bits per joule} and compared against transformer and neuromorphic baselines.
  \item \textbf{Ethical Coherence:} Mean $U_{\text{ethos}}$ across diverse simulated societies; monitored for drift or bias.
\end{enumerate}

