% =========================
% Implementation Plan
% =========================
\section{Implementation Plan}
\label{sec:implementation}
\subsection{Development Roadmap}
We outline a pragmatic path from theoretical framework to deployed system:

\paragraph{Phase 0: Simulation Environment (6--12 months)}
Build \textbf{Aetherion-Core}, a Python/Rust hybrid simulation implementing:
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item Micro-mind substrate with event-driven messaging (Rust for performance)
  \item Router and sparse activation logic (PyTorch backend)
  \item Energy accounting and Ethos Core constraint solver (Python)
  \item Synthetic task generators for ACTD benchmark
\end{itemize}
\emph{Deliverable:} Open-source repository enabling community replication of results.

\paragraph{Phase 1: Robotic Integration (12--18 months)}
Deploy Aetherion-Core on small-scale robotic platforms:
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item Embedded systems (NVIDIA Jetson, edge TPUs) for real-time control
  \item Integration with ROS2 for perception and actuation
  \item Energy telemetry from battery-powered operation
  \item Validation of energy efficiency claims ($\eta \approx 10^{-7}$)
\end{itemize}
\emph{Deliverable:} Proof-of-concept demonstrating biological-level efficiency on physical tasks.

\paragraph{Phase 2: Distributed Cloud Cognition (18--30 months)}
Scale to multi-node cloud infrastructure:
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item Kubernetes orchestration for micro-mind swarms
  \item Ray/Dask for distributed memory fabric
  \item Federated learning for decentralized evolution
  \item Multi-institutional signing protocol for governance
\end{itemize}
\emph{Deliverable:} 1000-node cognitive mesh handling complex multi-agent reasoning.

\paragraph{Phase 3: Autonomous Systems Deployment (30--48 months)}
Gradual integration into real-world applications:
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item Scientific discovery assistants (drug design, theorem proving)
  \item Industrial process optimization (supply chain, energy grids)
  \item Educational co-tutors with human-aligned explanations
  \item Continuous monitoring by international oversight board
\end{itemize}
\emph{Deliverable:} Production-ready ASI serving humanity-scale problems.

\subsection{Software Architecture Overview}
Figure~\ref{fig:arch-impl} shows the layered implementation architecture.

