\subsection{Technology Stack}
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item \textbf{Core Runtime:} Rust (low-level performance) + Python (research flexibility)
  \item \textbf{ML Framework:} PyTorch 2.0+ with compile optimizations
  \item \textbf{Distributed Compute:} Ray for multi-node coordination
  \item \textbf{Memory Systems:} Redis (event routing), Qdrant (vector search)
  \item \textbf{Orchestration:} Kubernetes with custom operators for micro-mind scaling
  \item \textbf{Monitoring:} Prometheus (metrics), Grafana (dashboards), distributed tracing (Jaeger)
  \item \textbf{Security:} CRYSTALS-Dilithium signatures, SGX enclaves for Ethos Core isolation
\end{itemize}

