\section{Experimental Simulations and Validation}
\label{sec:experiments}

\subsection{Thermodynamic Simulation of Ethical Convergence}

We simulated 1000 micro-minds evolving under the Aetherion Equation over 10,000 iterations. Each mind started with random $\theta_m$ and ethical divergence $D_m \sim \mathcal{U}(0.3, 0.8)$.

\begin{figure}[H]
\centering
\begin{tikzpicture}
\begin{axis}[
    width=0.9\linewidth,
    height=6.5cm,
    xlabel={Iteration $t$},
